*Analysts say 'cloudy' forecast is OK
http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/originalContent/0,289142,sid14_gci1095562,00.html?track=NL-358&ad=519329
Gartner Security Summit analysts predict security will move off
networks and into the Internet cloud. 

*Trojan trio disables Windows, AV updates
http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/originalContent/0,289142,sid14_gci1094469,00.html?track=NL-358&ad=519329
Three Trojan horse programs collaborate to hijack as many machines as
possible. Their goal: access bank account numbers, steal identities
and more.

